text: Sheikh Mujibur Rahman is a Bangladeshi politician. He is a member of the Bangladesh Nationalist Party . He was elected a member of parliament from Bagerhat-1 in February 1996. == Career == Prafulla Kumar Mandal was elected to parliament from Bagerhat-1 as a Bangladesh Nationalist Party candidate in 15 February 1996 Bangladeshi general election. He was defeated from Bagerhat-1 constituency on 12 June 1996 and 2001 on the nomination of Bangladesh Nationalist Party. == References == Category:Politicians from Khulna Division Category:Living people Category:6th Jatiya Sangsad members
title: Sheikh Mujibur Rahman (politician)
